OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNHS Wales: 'I spent four   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnights in A&E waiting for a
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbed'                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, When John Evans needed treatment for a 
OL,6, rapidly spreading skin infection on his
OL,7, face, he was told to go to A&E.        
OL,9,F"It's happened to me before, so I knew 
OL,10,FI had to get some serious treatments   
OL,11,Fand IV antibiotics," said the          
OL,12,F59-year-old from Cardiff.              
OL,14,FBut he said he spent four nights on a  
OL,15,Fchair at Cardiff's University Hospital 
OL,16,Fof Wales waiting for a bed.            
OL,18,FCardiff and Vale health board said it  
OL,19,Fwas in touch with Mr Evans and         
OL,20,F"sincerely" apologised.                
